<h2 class="govuk-heading-m">
  Apply for targeted retention incentive payment each academic year
</h2>

<p class="govuk-body">
  So long as your circumstances stay the same, you could claim for
  targeted retention incentive payments in future academic years. This depends
  on the years you studied or when you began teaching.
</p>

<h3 class="govuk-heading-s">Set a reminder to apply next year</h3>

<p class="govuk-body">
  Receive a reminder email so you know when you can apply next year. We
  cannot issue payments unless you apply.
</p>

<%= govuk_button_link_to(
  "Set reminder",
  reminder_path(journey: journey.routing_name, slug: "personal-details")
) %>
